org.jetel.hadoop.connection

Class HadoopProvidersFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.hadoop.connection.HadoopProvidersFactory

  • public final class HadoopProvidersFactory
extends java.lang.Object

    Static factory class for instantiating providers for Hadoop services of required Hadoop API version. It also supports other version related operations like providing list of supported Hadoop API versions. Together with service layer this class allows abstraction from different Hadoop API versions.

    This class also creates a proxy (a wrapper class that delegates all the methods to the wrapped, original provider) for each service before returning it. This proxy classes ensure that providers methods are called in correct context - that is with the right context class loader set (see Thread.setContextClassLoader(ClassLoader)). Proxy classes are private and therefore invisible to client nor does the provider implementation recognize that its method are beeing called through proxy.

    This class contains static factory methods for creating providers of these services for required Hadoop API versions:

    • HadoopConnectingFileSystemService
    • HadoopConnectingMapReduceService
    • HadoopMapReduceInfoService

    Since:
    rel-3-4-0-M2
